Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.52,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:08.84,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,If he's the type to accept one girl's chocolate and then go off holding another girl's hand,{Did I just turn "cocolate" into some
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.59,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,it's probably better if she doesn't get along with him.{bah this is terrible too}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Uh... Onee-chan, here it is!
Comment: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! 10 yen! You were right!{DEUS FUCKING EX FUCKING MACHINA}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Onee-chan... You actually found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You're the amazing one for finding it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Anyway, let's hurry up and go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:52.16,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Please, just walk past the store while we're inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... are these pork buns really 10 yen each?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am. We're currently in the middle of a promotional campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Two, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:06.69,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But if she were to see a him holding hands with someone else or something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:11.01,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan probably wouldn't like him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means I'd--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.48,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Something I can do... for Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, it's the perfect chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's buy two more pork buns! We can each have two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great! The two of you are getting along well!{the two of you have gotten together}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran away without explaining anything, so I was worried that things wouldn't turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great, great!{That's great!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{If something happens later, tell me.}I you ever need help, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, I was asked to give him that chocolate on her behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.50,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I completely jumped to conclusions and ended up making a big deal out of nothing.{a mountain out of a molehill}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it caused a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know, Asu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you're worried that something like that might happen in the future, remember this:{suspicious : usage}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will never abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:20:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That said, I think the fact that you\Nwere so jealous made me a little happy.{ITE: Kyou is a sadist}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care.{I wasn't jealous!}{I DON'T KNOW AND I FEEL NOTHING}{TSUNDERE ASUCHAN}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry! Are you mad?{u mad bro}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.11,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,It's things like worrying about someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.75,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,bringing them{him or her} a warm coat to wear,{Bringing that person a warm coat to wear...}{getting that nice and warm feeling inside because of it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.97,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,and going to find cheap pork buns just so\Nyou'll be able to eat them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:30.79,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,When I think that one day, Onee-chan will do those things with someone besides me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.10,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I can't help but feel a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:41.06,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I think that even when that time comes, Onee-chan will assume me I won't be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.83,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But is that something I can just answer, "Okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.65,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe, when that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who might this chocolate be intended for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My favorite person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! And who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up! Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is your favorite person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:21.85,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, I'll definitely choose whatever makes my favorite sister happy.{OH GODDAMN FUCK}
